{
  "stem": "15028.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Everybody recognized their own top from the-- from the bakery.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And for Saturday-- we had a [INAUDIBLE] in town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And Saturday, they went-- the kids went, and brought home, and they knew which top to bring on the cholent.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "On-- and like I said, my father had a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So did the [NON-ENGLISH], and so did the rabbi.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Everybody had that uniform, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were-- in the family, we were nine children, and Father, and Mother.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We had-- we were six brothers and three sisters.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] there was no way, where to go, what-- for where to leave.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the trouble started in-- I would say 1940 or '41.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The trouble started in '36, when they, for a short period, when they were in the towns and throw Jews out of the trains in Romania, and anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were writing, in-- in different butcher's stores, [NON-ENGLISH], Jewish meat is cheap, or something translation in Romanian.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I felt, as a child at that time-- that time we had in school, and we had fights with kids, and anti-Semitism started very, very strong, really.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In 1940 or '41, we were under the Romania-- Romanian government.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And Hitler, somehow, now what I understand, gave back the piece of land to the Transylvania, to the Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, the Hungarians always blamed that that belonged to them, that somehow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "One day, I remember the Hungarian soldiers, gendarmes, marched into town and took over this whole area, and became Hungary.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Romanian gendarmes moved out from the town and became Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that-- that year, or a year or two years, was very, very rough, as far as food, clothing and food, food.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We suffered a lot about hunger.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
